title: Is Age Just a Number? | The Answer
description:
Chris and Seerat discuss how the best teams in the league are getting a lot of help from older veterans and how the prime of NBA players appears to be older than what it used to be.

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Seerat Sohi
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
